    "meta_description": "\'93Christ Is Mine Forevermore\'94 by CityAlight is a worship song offering hope amid trials, focusing on our eternal inheritance in Jesus. Learn about its biblical foundations in Scripture, its message of enduring hope and joy, and how to effectively lead this song to encourage your congregation."\
